title: By the King and Queen, a proclamation William R.
author: England and Wales. Sovereign (1689-1694 : William and Mary)
publisher: Printed by Charles Bill and Thomas Newcomb ...,
notes: Reproduction of original in Huntington Library.
At end of text: Given at our court at Whitehall this 16th day of March, in the first year of our reign.
Orders the suppression of rebellious soldiers.
